I"<h1 id="task">Task</h1>

<h2 id="syntax">Syntax</h2>

<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="s2">"task"</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">boolean</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="nv">$value</span> <span class="c1">// default true</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<p>Task lists allow you to create a list of items with checkboxes. checkboxes will be displayed next to the content. To create a task list, add dashes (-) and brackets with a space ([ ]) in front of task list items. To select a checkbox, add an x in between the brackets ([x]).</p>

<div class="code-example">
<ul class="task-list">
  <li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" class="task-list-item-checkbox" disabled="disabled" checked="checked" />Write the press release</li>
  <li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" class="task-list-item-checkbox" disabled="disabled" />Update the website</li>
  <li class="task-list-item"><input type="checkbox" class="task-list-item-checkbox" disabled="disabled" />Contact the media</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="language-markdown highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="p">-</span> [x] Write the press release
<span class="p">-</span> [ ] Update the website
<span class="p">-</span> [ ] Contact the media
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="examples">Examples</h2>

<h3 id="disable">Disable</h3>
<p>Disable tables</p>

<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$Parsedown</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="k">new</span> <span class="nc">ParsedownExtended</span><span class="p">([</span>
    <span class="s1">'lists'</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">{</span>
        <span class="s1">'task'</span> <span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="kc">false</span>
    <span class="p">}</span>
<span class="p">]);</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
